Show HN: Watch a playlist of YouTube videos with other people at the same time
text:
I created a community that cycles through a playlist of YouTube videos and synchronizes the playback so people can watch and chat about it together at the same time.

The inspiration for the app initially came from an old and now defunct website called SynchTube where there were public rooms you could join and the participants would all watch the same video at the same time. I always thought it was a unique viewing experience and wanted to replicate something similar with my own app.

The app Sociables (https://sociables.com/creators) is actually targeted towards content creators however lends well for all types of communities.
